| Entity        | Attributes                                                           |
| ------------- | -------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| **Product**   | `product_id`, `name`, `description`, `price`, `stock_quantity`       |
| **Customer**  | `customer_id`, `name`, `email`, `phone`                              |
| **Order**     | `order_id`, `customer_id`, `order_date`, `total_amount`              |
| **OrderItem** | `order_item_id`, `order_id`, `product_id`, `quantity`, `price`       |
| **Payment**   | `payment_id`, `order_id`, `payment_date`, `amount`, `payment_method` |
